          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Basically this is not a school it is an educational shop. Their motive is only to make profit out of Parents pocket. Very pathetic management. Almost every notice comes on the 11th hour. All staff is new, they don't know how to run the school.\nPrincipal - This position is only for name sake, Principal does not have any authority, She is not able to solve any reported problem. Basically it is co-ordinator role with Label Principal.\nEducation material is good but they don't cover all Syllabus available in Material.\nUltimately, OIS is Very costly school which provides very poor quality education, poor quality uniform, bag and shoes and only frustration to parents though out the year.\nI advise to avoid this school.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
