            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "School staff doesn't have the capability to plan and manage the amount of admissions that they have taken. Making sure the kids enter the school premises itself is a struggle. Total mismanagement and chaos. School did not even arrange a parent's meeting to inform how they should prepare the kids for the school what books to be sent, how they should be labeled. At the school gate you have to push yourself and your kid through a large crowd to make sure your kid enters the school. See attached pictures for reference.\nOrchids management, please take some corrective action to avoid this chaos.",
